Class FreeMarkerMailHandlerReminder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.util.event.FreeMarkerMailHandlerReminder

    IEventSubscriber

    public class FreeMarkerMailHandlerReminder
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEventSubscriber
    Mail handler listener for reminder e-mails for due or overdue items. It is being called from the EmailReminderJob.
